This is a set of instructions for pairing bluetooth via 
Terminal

systemctl status bluetooth

systemctl start bluetooth


edit config file for bluetooth /etc/bluetooth/main.conf
sudo vi /etc/bluetooth/main.conf

Look for the ControllerMode and set to bredr
restart Bluetooth
sudo /etc/init.d/bluetooth restart

Use bluetoothctl 
After prompted type scan on
pair <Airpod Name Here>

done
